'''''Roma wa la n'toura''''' (Icyongereza: '''''Rome Rather Than You'''''; Igifaransa: '''''Rome plutôt que vous''''' ) ni filime y’ikinamico yo muri 2006 yakorewe muri [[Alijeriya]]-[[Igifaransa|abafaransa]] [[Ubudage|n’Ubudage]] iyobowe na Tariq Teguia  ikinwamo na Samira Kaddour na Rachid Amrani nk’urubyiruko babiri bashaka kuva muri Alijeriya n'intambara y'abenegihugu ya Alijeriya kugira ngo bagire ejo hazaza heza<ref>ROMA WA LA N'TOUMA | Library of Congress (loc.gov)</ref><ref>ROMA WA LA N'TOUMA | Viennale <nowiki>https://www.viennale.at</nowiki> › films › roma-wa-la-ntouma</ref>.  Nibikorwa bya Teguia byerekanwe bwa mbere.<ref>Roma ao invés de você (hrvwiki.net)</ref>  (Yabanje gukora filime ngufi na documentaire ya 2002.  ) Filime yatsindiye igihembo cyihariye cyabacamanza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Friborg 2007.<ref>rome rather than you (moosejawmortgagebroker.com)</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Kamel w'imyaka 20 n'inshuti ye, Zina w'imyaka makumyabiri n'itatu, bashakisha muri [[Alijeriya]] Bosco ucuruza abantu  kugira ngo babone pasiporo mpimbano kugira ngo bashobore kuva mu gihugu berekeza i Roma<ref>rome rather than you (anna-kazantseva.com)</ref>.

== Kwakira ==
''Abanenga ibinyamakuru bitandukanye,'' Robert Koehler yashimye "Umukinnyi wa mbere wa Tariq Teguia.<ref>L'Algérie des Généreux - Africiné <nowiki>http://africine.org</nowiki> › evenement › lalg...</ref> . . Nubwo ibihe bya nyuma biteganijwe, kugerayo ndetse na nyuma yacyo byerekana Teguia kuba umuyobozi w’amasezerano akomeye "<ref>L'Algérie des Généreux - Africiné <nowiki>http://africine.org</nowiki> › evenement › lalg...</ref>.  Koehler yemeje kandi "ibihangano bisanzwe, byoroshye imikorere" ya Kaddoui na Amrani. <ref>Roy Merath Facebook, Twitter & MySpace on PeekYou <nowiki>https://www.peekyou.com</nowiki> › roy_merath</ref> Mu ''kinyamakuru Slant'', ariko, Eric Henderson yabonaga ko iyi filime "yatekerejwe mu bwirasi, yiyitirira ko yakozwe, kandi ikaba ndende<ref>Rome Rather Than You – Films - Visions du Réel <nowiki>https://www.visionsdureel.ch</nowiki> › ... › Atelier Tariq Teguia</ref>". 

